{"tid":2337362,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"★港股圓頂派發？大跌市快來臨","createTime":"2020-12-23T08:37:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-23T09:26:10.000Z","uid":19454,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"13bb5eebaad96aaa14f69d107b5597b0a76456e0","tid":2337362,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:37:10.000Z","msg":"長假前交投轉靜影響承接力，若短線確認失守26,000點關，估計仲有得跌！<br />\n<br />\n技術上，上周恒指10日線失守20日線，已是一個利淡訊號，再加上如今正在考驗11月上旬的上升裂口位(25,800至26,000點水平)，若短線此位一失，基本上可確認港股完成為時逾月的圓頂派發，向下兩大支持位在25,000及24,000點關。<br />\n不過，宜留意今次港股調整，成交縮減，理論上沽壓並非想像中大，暫可看待成短期調整，未有大散水之虞。畢竟仲有大把中企排隊來港上市，若然港股大冧，那不少中企的海外融資計劃都會受到影響。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201223/bkn-20201223080044383-1223_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20201223%2Fbkn-20201223080044383-1223_00842_001.html&d=djscsuFvXcghIMf2lgFVp%2FrgBFspSC5jYnxvlVik22g%3D&h=37e66c77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20201223/bkn-20201223080044383-1223_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"ebee3c36007b9bdcd8c0675046071b07df87f90a","tid":2337362,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:37:35.000Z","msg":"down down down<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cca8bb57a2f28707ce4bb88035a78e0bd216b703","tid":2337362,"uid":5178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:40:35.000Z","msg":"唔洗諗啦<br />\n盤後期指已經升緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e72dec9323a6d109dff47a7a73484aed13019363","tid":2337362,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-23T08:41:43.000Z